{"type":null,"faqId":45213,"title":"如何使用B2解锁？","answer":"<p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:51.05pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';line-height:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\n'微软雅黑','sans-serif';color:black;\">B2</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';color:black;\">解锁能够帮您免除手机复杂的解锁方式，将蓝牙设备移动到手机旁，轻按手机电源，即可免密码锁手机。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:51.05pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';line-height:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\ncolor:black;\">使用<span>B2</span>智能解锁需要有一款拥有此功能的华为手机和一台蓝牙设备，蓝牙设备包括蓝牙耳机，手环等。此处以蓝牙耳机为例，设置<span>B2</span>智能解锁操作步骤如下：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:51.05pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';line-height:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\n'微软雅黑','sans-serif';color:black;\">1. </span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';color:black;\">进入“设置”，选择“锁屏和密码”，进入“锁屏密码”设置您的手机密码（若您的手机已设置密码请忽略该步骤）；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:51.05pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';line-height:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\n'微软雅黑','sans-serif';color:black;\">2. </span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';color:black;\">点击“设置”\n选择“锁屏和密码”，点击进入“智能解锁，如下图所示：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:51.05pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\nline-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';color:black;\"><img width=\"178\" height=\"316\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150917091105982001.gif\"><img width=\"176\" height=\"315\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150917091105833002.gif\"><img width=\"177\" height=\"316\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150917091105343003.gif\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\nline-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\ncolor:black;layout-grid-mode:both\">3. </span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\ncolor:black;layout-grid-mode:both\">输入您之前设置的锁屏密码，进入智能解锁设置界面，连接您的蓝牙设备，如下图所示：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:51.05pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\nline-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';color:black;\"><img width=\"172\" height=\"306\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150917091105410004.gif\"><img width=\"172\" height=\"306\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150917091105568005.jpg\"><img width=\"174\" height=\"309\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150917091105642006.gif\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\nline-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\ncolor:black;layout-grid-mode:both\">4. </span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\ncolor:black;layout-grid-mode:both\">选择“添加用于解锁的设备“，开启”智能解锁“，选择您第<span>3</span>步中连接上的蓝牙设备，如下图所示：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:51.05pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\ntext-indent:47.25pt;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';color:black;\n\"><img width=\"180\" height=\"321\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150917091105118007.gif\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><img width=\"183\" height=\"321\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150917091105348008.gif\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\nline-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\ncolor:black;layout-grid-mode:both\">5. </span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\ncolor:black;layout-grid-mode:both\">全部设置完成后，您的蓝牙耳机在手机附件时能面密码解锁。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:51.05pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\ntext-indent:21.0pt;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'\">注：若有多个蓝牙设备连接到手机，这些设备都能实现<span>B2</span>智能解锁功能。</span></p>\n<br>\n</p>","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"713","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442451578000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10,CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":107,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"B2,手机,解锁","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}